<p>This endpoint retrieves users leaderboard for a specific period. It includes an array of user object (<code>target</code>) and their score (<code>total</code>).</p>
<h3 id='http-request-17'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code class="request">GET /api/v1/stats/users/leaderboard</code></p>
<h3 id='query-parameters-2'>Query Parameters</h3>
